  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F).",
    "Rinse the trout fillets and pat them dry with paper towels.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together kosher salt, black pepper, and olive oil.",
    "Brush the nuka-pickle brine evenly over both sides of the trout fillets.",
